PrecisRegulations Amending the PROCESSED PRODUCTS REGULATIONS which allow for the sale of frozen French-fried potatoes in packages weighing between two and 20 kilograms, without any restrictions as to increments within that range, and will eliminate standardized package sizes for other frozen potato products and for ripe black olives.
